{"tid":2495561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奶貓寵物展無故遭柴犬咬斷頸骨死亡  狗主反駁後不顧而去：我啲狗不嬲會咬貓","createTime":"2021-04-19T09:01:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T14:40:42.000Z","uid":358086,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"a4272c62da124e24681f70a57f3f742f2408396c","tid":2495561,"uid":358086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:01:51.000Z","msg":"2021年寵物節早前於灣仔會展舉行，展覽有售各款寵物零食及用品，吸引了不少有養寵物的主人前往到場，場面非常熱鬧。不過在展覽發生一些不愉快事件，有養貓的主人因要照顧奶貓，所以帶牠到會場上班，可是遭其他寵物咬死。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZYwoicDyDri84ZGPqGS3wcR43y5KoW7wJRkhp7Wfsjj5?filename=B6wQq9C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB6wQq9C.png&h=fa818ad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事主在Facebook群組「天下貓貓一樣貓」發文，講到貓BB還細，所以要帶牠到會展上班方便餵奶，當時用單肩袋帶住貓B，可是會場有有一男一女用2架寵物車帶住4隻柴犬，其中有一隻柴犬見到貓B，於是探進袋內並咬住貓B。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSgAKtDcz8oPvpJ7opHHnZP8n9vN2eJPiHLsugbdkBunu?filename=3FNHhgw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3FNHhgw.png&h=0b823ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZjdZFrNYcig3X24GXWKeZeVELUFW884XucWZqH8FDXiZ?filename=PgYZ3WA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgYZ3WA.png&h=37ab9997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事主形容當時該柴犬「咬住貓貓嚟揈（Fing），令貓貓頸骨斷咗而死。」該兩名主人得悉後，竟表示：「隻狗不嬲會咬貓」而該兩名主人明知其寵物會咬貓，亦沒有幫柴犬戴上口罩，發生事後亦不顧而去。事主現希望網民告知狗主資料，並盡一切努力去追究。<br />\n<br />\n據知事主報警後，警方要求事主向律師要求會展方面提供CCTV。網民亦對此進行人肉搜索，疑找出肇事狗主的IG，同時亦有在場人士目擊事發經過，表示聽到狗主人回應：「買返隻貓畀你都無補於事啦！」而網上的反應兩極，除了大罵狗主不負責任之外，亦有人責怪受害者，指她帶貓出街，就要承受意外發生的風險，隨即引起了罵戰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQDeL47dcS4cf8YAxaUVarizzdWf8QPhUYTJ29sJoCHmR?filename=C77PGJk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC77PGJk.png&h=cda5ae99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/215036/寵物展2021-奶貓無故遭柴犬咬斷頸骨死亡-狗主反駁後不顧而去-我啲狗不嬲會咬貓/2?utm_source=instagram-story&amp;utm_medium=social\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F215036%2F%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9%E5%B1%952021-%E5%A5%B6%E8%B2%93%E7%84%A1%E6%95%85%E9%81%AD%E6%9F%B4%E7%8A%AC%E5%92%AC%E6%96%B7%E9%A0%B8%E9%AA%A8%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1-%E7%8B%97%E4%B8%BB%E5%8F%8D%E9%A7%81%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%8D%E9%A1%A7%E8%80%8C%E5%8E%BB-%E6%88%91%E5%95%B2%E7%8B%97%E4%B8%8D%E5%AC%B2%E6%9C%83%E5%92%AC%E8%B2%93%2F2%3Futm_source%3Dinstagram-story%26utm_medium%3Dsocial&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=fb247fb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/215036/寵物展2021-奶貓無故遭柴犬咬斷頸骨死亡-狗主反駁後不顧而去-我啲狗不嬲會咬貓/2?utm_source=instagram-story&amp;utm_medium=social</a>"},{"pid":"464ed798a2ce3259dd11b3651891a2b722620a7b","tid":2495561,"uid":375068,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:03:17.000Z","msg":"條友正冚家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4874094ab7e8dba5d6ed03800def248428a72faa","tid":2495561,"uid":133806,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.spca.org.hk/images/companions/rabies3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spca.org.hk%2Fimages%2Fcompanions%2Frabies3.jpg&h=77097e01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n應該搵漁護署捉隻主人去檢疫"},{"pid":"f9aedc08ce87c269436b70a008ad2a0c19b387c4","tid":2495561,"uid":389289,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"佢生左個仔 個仔殺左人 會唔會話 我個仔不嬲都會殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee817a64eaa48632201db2ac97c0db89c84f0cf","tid":2495561,"uid":143241,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:16:20.000Z","msg":"報狗冇用,啲狗唔會拉自己人"},{"pid":"eafa08b2fd898dca9ce09b33ffa3bd2337f6c198","tid":2495561,"uid":59037,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:40:49.000Z","msg":"黑警真係垃撚圾，明明自己都拎到cctv，而家唔想煩就叫律師